headline: 3 Reasons to Sell MDLZ and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Mondelez has had an impressive run over the past six months as its shares have beaten the S&P 500 by 11.6%. The stock now trades at $67.14, marking a 16% gain. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
